{"tid":1392818,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"近視嘅手足可以試吓自己改裝眼鏡","createTime":"2019-08-01T01:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T05:27:38.000Z","uid":263902,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f57c68eb0ef8a538e9c38940cef86e0c20c5dc7","tid":1392818,"uid":263902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:06:48.000Z","msg":"唔好意思第一次出post有咩錯漏請見諒<br />\n<br />\n自己本身戴眼鏡，再戴個封左氣孔嘅3M眼罩，但眼鏡頂住唔貼面點都入到煙<br />\nOTG護目鏡同有度數泳鏡都唔太平<br />\n我諗戴眼鏡嘅大家屋企總有一兩副舊眼鏡<br />\n一於循環再用改裝下佢<br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n1副舊眼鏡（我係用冇鼻托嘅眼鏡）<br />\n2隻萬字夾<br />\n1條粗橡筋帶<br />\n<br />\n工具：<br />\n眼鏡螺絲批<br />\n針線<br />\n2隻魚尾夾／扣針<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OmwZnZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmwZnZc.jpg&h=b7b9f857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做法：<br />\n先用螺絲批拆左兩雙鏡臂出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQAO0L8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQAO0L8.jpg&h=b3e04da6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後用萬字夾從下而上穿入螺絲孔，再轉至右圖方向<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0r5WqcY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0r5WqcY.jpg&h=cfc30b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意盡量將萬字夾維持垂直方向<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4t80MG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4t80MG.jpg&h=99a4b5f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n橡筋帶穿過一邊萬字夾，先用魚尾夾或扣針固定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/znNUWkc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FznNUWkc.jpg&h=92d23b70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n穿埋另一邊，戴住嚟度返要幾長，同樣用用魚尾夾或扣針固定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1YgB9Fm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1YgB9Fm.jpg&h=4d166f3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用針線聯返十針八針固定<br />\n（唔就手可以拆返晒啲萬字夾出嚟，聯完先再重組）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Br9j7sm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBr9j7sm.jpg&h=1cd55f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完成<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1zmq20O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1zmq20O.jpg&h=d817a9fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意：<br />\n如果橡筋帶套喺萬字夾嘅位置太高，眼鏡會向上反<br />\n要套較低位置，比較維持到正常配戴角度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oKx9Lej.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoKx9Lej.jpg&h=778bbc2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n效果：<br />\n－舊眼鏡度數無咁足，但夠用<br />\n－眼鏡本身冇鼻托，配合橡筋帶變得好貼臉，唔易移位<br />\n－冇左兩條鏡臂，外加眼罩無障礙<br />\n<br />\n無法解決：<br />\n冇鏡臂阻住，眼罩的確比之前更貼面<br />\n但大家面型唔同，例如我本身面型比較窄，淨戴眼罩本身就唔貼面<br />\n<br />\n不確定因素：<br />\n－如果配戴氣密眼罩，唔知會唔會影響到氣密效果<br />\n－我係用冇鼻托嘅眼鏡改，未能測試埋有鼻托眼鏡嘅效果<br />\n（如果有人試改有鼻托眼鏡，可以分享吓）<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到少少戴眼鏡嘅手足"},{"pid":"149aaef9292250a0670dc5a9d810a2e2008a190b","tid":1392818,"uid":9193,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9029277c1589e9a7f6cc146a93a8c188beb48c","tid":1392818,"uid":22009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:24:42.000Z","msg":"幫你推番上去 有用post"},{"pid":"2a6d91bf6fb2e74f1e9a315b6579eec82509128a","tid":1392818,"uid":59804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:27:38.000Z","msg":"我係諗有冇可能裝CAM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}